  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a swift action, you cause flaming shards of rock to erupt from your body. These shards deal 1d6 points of damage per 2 oracle levels (minimum 1d6) to all creatures in a 10-foot-radius burst (Reflex half ). Half of this damage is fire damage and the other half is piercing damage. The shards create difficult terrain for 1 round.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day at 5th level and every 5 levels thereafter.</p>"
